        {
          "fields": {
            "Name": "checkin_questions",
            "DisplayName": "Check-in Questions",
            "Description": "PropFuel check-in question (Q&A) records from the scheduled data-export file feed. Mutable upsert-with-soft-delete stream: a record is created when a question is sent, updated in place when the contact answers (answered_at / response / rating / selection fill), and soft-deleted (deleted_at set) on bot-click detection or multiple answers. Sourced from list->download .json files named [microtime]-checkin_questions.json. Live-proven: 838 files, 2318-record lifecycle scan (518 answered, 517 updated, 1 recurring identity).",
